#      Specifies Ffmpeg's include directory.
#
#   FFMPEG_LIBRARIES
#     Specifies Ffmpeg libraries that should be passed to target_link_libararies.
#
#   FFMPEG_<COMPONENT>_LIBRARIES
#     Specifies the libraries of a specific <COMPONENT>.
